title: ONESYNC_ENABLE_REMOTE_ATTACHMENT_SANITIZATION
content:
0x30CE39D8// OnesyncEnableRemoteAttachmentSanitization
void ONESYNC_ENABLE_REMOTE_ATTACHMENT_SANITIZATION(BOOL enable);Parameters:enable: Whether to enable sanitization.Toggles a check that prevents attaching (networked) entities to remotely owned peds. This is disabled by default.
